WEBVTT

00:52.886 --> 00:53.636
Oh!

00:55.055 --> 00:57.098
Yeah, ha-ha-ha, yeah!

00:57.182 --> 00:58.183
Hey! Ha-ha-ha!

00:59.517 --> 01:01.102
Yeah!

01:01.186 --> 01:02.729
Hey!

01:02.812 --> 01:07.108
Yeah-ha!

02:36.448 --> 02:38.074
- Oh, it's so beautiful
out here today.

02:38.158 --> 02:40.618
- Yeah, sure is.

02:40.702 --> 02:43.621
- Oh, did you see the ray?
- Yeah, huge.

02:43.705 --> 02:45.290
- Look what I got.
- Whoa, nice.

02:49.127 --> 02:50.670
Hey.

02:50.754 --> 02:51.629
- Hey

02:51.713 --> 02:53.882
- Look what I scored.

02:55.342 --> 02:58.219
What? How did you do that?

02:58.303 --> 03:00.263
- You need to learn
the way of the fish.

03:01.056 --> 03:02.640
- Having fun, sis?

03:02.724 --> 03:04.309
- Yeah.
- Group shot.

03:06.311 --> 03:08.313
All right, okay, you ready?
- Mm-hmm.

03:08.396 --> 03:11.066
- Yeah.
- One, two, three, smile.

03:16.321 --> 03:18.073
- That was so much fun.

03:19.657 --> 03:21.618
I'm so glad you got
me back into diving.

03:21.701 --> 03:23.119
- You're a natural.

03:23.203 --> 03:24.037
- Like you?

03:28.083 --> 03:28.875
Hey, what's that?

03:29.918 --> 03:31.211
- Oh, I don't know.
- How good

03:31.294 --> 03:33.171
are the islands going to be?

03:33.254 --> 03:35.048
- I know, right?

03:35.131 --> 03:37.258
The tropical water,
all that sunshine,

03:37.342 --> 03:38.510
fish everywhere.
- Mm, yeah.

03:38.593 --> 03:40.303
- Can't wait.

03:40.387 --> 03:42.389
- Greg come around to it yet?

03:42.472 --> 03:43.973
- Not really.
- Come on.

03:44.057 --> 03:47.143
It's just like book club only
with fish and spear guns.

03:47.227 --> 03:48.645
He gets that, doesn't he?

03:48.728 --> 03:50.855
- Sort of.
- Hmm.

03:50.939 --> 03:53.274
He'll come around to
it once he realizes

03:53.358 --> 03:55.193
what it means to you.

03:55.276 --> 03:56.111
- Isn't that Greg?

03:57.779 --> 03:59.239
- Yeah, it is.

04:06.913 --> 04:08.832
- Hey, babe. Ladies.

04:10.041 --> 04:11.418
- What are you doing here?

04:11.501 --> 04:13.503
- Well, that's
a nice way to greet the guy

04:13.586 --> 04:14.963
who's come to give
you a ride home.

04:15.046 --> 04:16.464
- But I said I had a lift.

04:18.675 --> 04:20.260
- Okay, well, I
thought it'd be nice

04:20.343 --> 04:21.302
to pick you up myself.

04:25.390 --> 04:26.182
- Thank you.

04:27.100 --> 04:27.892
- See you, sis.

04:30.311 --> 04:31.688
- See you guys.
- See ya.

04:46.202 --> 04:50.290
- God, will you get it
through your fucking head?

04:53.752 --> 04:54.544
Get in!

05:08.266 --> 05:10.643
- Hey, this is Cath.
Leave a message, bye.

05:12.270 --> 05:14.856
- Hey, sis. Uh, hope all's okay.

05:14.939 --> 05:17.442
Um, just give me a ring. Bye.

05:30.330 --> 05:31.373
Hey.

05:32.290 --> 05:33.458
How was your day?

05:33.541 --> 05:34.626
- Hmm?

05:34.709 --> 05:36.878
- Have you left
the house at all?

05:36.961 --> 05:39.464
- Uh, well, I'm an exotic bloom,

05:39.547 --> 05:40.840
so I'm not meant to be outside.

05:40.924 --> 05:45.095
- Oh, okay, well, exotic bloom,

05:45.178 --> 05:47.972
like we agreed, if you're gonna
be staying here for a while,

05:48.056 --> 05:49.099
you need to be
pulling your weight.

05:49.182 --> 05:50.308
- You sound like mom.

05:52.894 --> 05:54.646
- Well, she has a point.

05:54.729 --> 05:56.314
- Look, I'm just
different. Okay?

05:56.398 --> 05:57.357
I'm not like you and Cath.

05:57.440 --> 05:58.233
- Mm-hmm.

06:09.285 --> 06:13.415
- Hey, I gotta go, but
I'll be back soon, okay?

06:20.422 --> 06:22.924
- Hey, this is Cath.
Leave a message, bye.

06:55.457 --> 06:56.166
- Hello?

07:16.603 --> 07:17.645
Greg?

07:24.277 --> 07:25.070
Greg?

07:36.623 --> 07:37.415
Greg?

07:43.380 --> 07:45.006
- She wouldn't listen.

07:48.093 --> 07:49.427
- Where's Cath?

07:50.387 --> 07:51.596
Where's my sister?

07:52.847 --> 07:54.224
- She made me do it.

08:02.273 --> 08:03.066
- Cath?

08:05.819 --> 08:06.611
Cath?

08:18.623 --> 08:19.666
Cath?

08:37.142 --> 08:40.102
Cath!

09:57.138 --> 09:59.849
- Hello.
- There she is!

09:59.933 --> 10:03.520
Aw.
- How are you?

10:03.603 --> 10:05.522
- Wow, look at you.

10:05.605 --> 10:07.774
Ah, Jodes, guess who's here?

10:10.151 --> 10:12.570
- Nic! We we starting to worry.

10:12.654 --> 10:14.280
I didn't know if you
got my last message

10:14.364 --> 10:15.615
about the change of address.

10:15.699 --> 10:17.033
- Oh, yeah. Sorry.

10:17.117 --> 10:19.577
It's, uh, hard getting
online in rural India.

10:19.661 --> 10:21.871
- India. How was that?

10:21.955 --> 10:22.997
- It was good.

10:24.833 --> 10:27.377
Well, I got something.

10:29.629 --> 10:31.297
Tequila?
- Ooh-ah!

10:31.381 --> 10:32.674
Party time.

10:34.759 --> 10:36.094
- It's so good to see you.

10:37.095 --> 10:38.263
- Yeah, you too.

10:40.056 --> 10:41.307
- It's amazing, isn't it?

10:43.852 --> 10:44.811
- Yeah, it is.

10:51.067 --> 10:52.694
- Yeah, I'll go get the drinks.

10:58.074 --> 10:59.868
- What do you
think? Is she okay?

11:05.749 --> 11:07.625
- At least she's here.

11:07.709 --> 11:08.501
- Yeah.

11:11.796 --> 11:12.964
- Ready?
- Ready.

11:17.260 --> 11:18.595
- Here you go

11:18.678 --> 11:19.596
- Oh, thanks.

11:21.765 --> 11:22.807
What? Annie.

11:25.018 --> 11:27.979
Oh my God. What
are you doing here?

11:28.063 --> 11:30.190
- I wanted to surprise you.

11:30.273 --> 11:33.485
- Huh. Yeah, you've
definitely done that.

11:34.652 --> 11:36.404
So what you're into diving now?

11:36.488 --> 11:38.156
- Well, yeah, sort of.

11:41.618 --> 11:42.369
- What's that?

11:43.912 --> 11:46.247
- Oh, that, we wanted
to talk to you about it.

11:50.001 --> 11:51.836
You know, coming here
was Cath's dream.

11:51.920 --> 11:53.755
So we thought it'd
be the perfect place

11:53.838 --> 11:54.714
to pay our tributes.

11:58.051 --> 11:59.219
We all thought it
was a good idea,

11:59.302 --> 12:00.637
but if you don't
think it's right then-

12:00.720 --> 12:05.934
- No, no, I'm sure
it's great.

12:07.227 --> 12:11.106
Uh, I'm kind of tired
from the long trip.

12:11.189 --> 12:11.981
Where's my room?

12:13.817 --> 12:18.279
- Yeah, I'll show you.

12:18.363 --> 12:19.155
- Hmm.

12:28.873 --> 12:30.500
Here you go.

12:30.583 --> 12:31.501
- Thanks.

13:17.380 --> 13:18.715
- Can I have the wine after you?

13:18.798 --> 13:20.925
- Yeah.
- Oof, look at you go.

13:21.009 --> 13:23.803
- Want some more.
- Yes.

13:23.887 --> 13:26.806
- Why don't we
make a toast here?

13:32.812 --> 13:33.605
Top up?

13:34.564 --> 13:35.690
- Oh, yeah, thank you.

13:38.818 --> 13:39.611
Hmm.

13:42.197 --> 13:43.782
What have you been up to?

13:43.865 --> 13:44.866
- Not much.

13:44.949 --> 13:47.660
Um, just working,
looking after mom.

13:50.038 --> 13:52.123
I made an apple
pie the other day.

13:52.207 --> 13:54.626
- What? You're cooking?

13:54.709 --> 13:57.003
That's great.

14:03.968 --> 14:05.428
- So is it true?

14:05.512 --> 14:07.764
You were working in the
Greek Islands on a dive boat?

14:07.847 --> 14:09.974
- Yeah.

14:10.058 --> 14:12.769
Yeah, taking happy
snaps of rich divers.

14:16.147 --> 14:18.942
But, um, yeah, it
didn't really work out.

14:21.903 --> 14:23.988
Stopped diving, actually.

14:26.574 --> 14:27.367
- Really?

14:28.827 --> 14:29.619
- Yeah.

14:33.873 --> 14:36.835
- Hey, come and help me
cook the marshmallows

14:36.918 --> 14:40.213
'cause I keep dropping
them in the fire.

14:40.296 --> 14:41.297
Watch out for that.

14:43.717 --> 14:44.968
Clutz.

14:47.137 --> 14:48.555
Here.

15:18.001 --> 15:21.046
- Three days of
paddling. Three days?

15:21.129 --> 15:22.380
I thought you said it was two.

15:22.464 --> 15:24.466
- It's two nights, but
three days paddling.

15:24.549 --> 15:26.426
Two days wouldn't
be worth coming for.

15:27.844 --> 15:28.928
- Three days of paddling.

15:30.555 --> 15:32.807
- Don't worry. We'll
take it easy on you.

15:32.891 --> 15:34.100
Won't we, Jodie?

15:34.184 --> 15:34.976
- Of course.

15:36.644 --> 15:39.064
- You did say that there was
gonna be a four-star resort.

15:39.147 --> 15:43.693
- There is, absolute luxury,
rising pool, cocktails.

15:43.777 --> 15:45.612
Everything a girl could want.

15:45.695 --> 15:46.863
That's the third night.

15:48.198 --> 15:50.075
- The third night? Great.

15:51.409 --> 15:52.202
- Here we go.

15:54.287 --> 15:55.413
- Look at that.
- Oh.

15:57.499 --> 15:59.209
Oh my God.
- Come on, slow pokes.

16:02.420 --> 16:06.758
- Let's go.

16:10.136 --> 16:11.930
- Okay, who wants what?

16:13.640 --> 16:15.266
Actually, Annie,
thinking about it,

16:15.350 --> 16:16.851
maybe you should take
one of the yellow ones.

16:16.935 --> 16:18.520
Easier to get in and out of.

16:18.603 --> 16:19.938
- Sure.
- Lisa,

16:20.021 --> 16:21.815
you'll take the
other yellow one.

16:24.359 --> 16:25.568
- Okay.

16:25.652 --> 16:27.445
- Okay. Let's get packing

16:27.529 --> 16:30.073
And remember to distribute
the weight evenly.

16:31.199 --> 16:32.492
- Is she always this alpha?

16:33.410 --> 16:36.037
- Mostly.

16:48.425 --> 16:49.467
- Okay. Let's go.

18:06.252 --> 18:09.089
- How are you? You okay?

18:09.172 --> 18:10.465
- Yeah.

18:10.548 --> 18:12.050
- You look tired.

18:12.133 --> 18:14.052
You wanna take a break?

18:14.135 --> 18:16.304
- No, I'm not really tired.
I don't need a break.

18:20.475 --> 18:24.229
- You know, Annie
don't get me wrong,

18:24.312 --> 18:26.231
it's great to see
you, it's just like

18:27.941 --> 18:29.317
this isn't really you.

18:32.237 --> 18:33.947
- You might be surprised.

18:36.616 --> 18:37.367
- Come on. I'll tow you.

18:37.450 --> 18:40.203
- I'm fine. Thanks.

18:47.585 --> 18:48.753
- Hmm.

18:56.469 --> 18:58.513
- Yeah,
this is the place.

18:58.596 --> 19:01.141
- Yes. Hey, we're
gonna go for a dive.

19:15.280 --> 19:17.282
- Oh. It's so beautiful.

19:34.174 --> 19:35.967
- Mm.
- Oh.

19:36.051 --> 19:36.843
- Hey.

19:38.511 --> 19:39.304
Ready?

19:40.430 --> 19:43.016
- Uh, I'm just
gonna float up here.

19:43.099 --> 19:44.309
- Come with us?

19:44.392 --> 19:45.185
- Okay.

19:50.273 --> 19:53.109
- Let's go over here for a bit.

20:00.408 --> 20:02.827
Nic, follow me down?

20:02.911 --> 20:04.329
- I'll come down in a minute.

20:04.412 --> 20:05.205
- Okay.

21:55.482 --> 21:56.316
- Oh, hey.
- Hi.

21:56.399 --> 21:57.484
- Can you help me get out?

21:57.567 --> 21:59.277
- Well, yeah, of course.

21:59.361 --> 22:00.362
- Okay.

22:00.445 --> 22:02.322
- I think I've
damaged my spearhead.

22:07.243 --> 22:09.287
- Hey, you coming down?

22:10.455 --> 22:12.499
- Oh, my sinuses are playing up.

22:12.582 --> 22:14.376
Think I'm coming
down with something.

22:16.169 --> 22:18.546
- Okay. See you soon?

22:18.630 --> 22:20.048
- Mm. Yeah.

22:20.131 --> 22:20.924
- Okay.

22:38.566 --> 22:42.028
- There's kids
swimming on that island.

22:48.576 --> 22:49.411
Wait, what's that?

22:51.579 --> 22:54.207
- Lots of fish around.
Must be a bait ball.

23:20.567 --> 23:21.359
Shit.

23:22.652 --> 23:24.487
- What?
- I think I saw a shark.

23:25.905 --> 23:27.449
- Was it big?

23:27.532 --> 23:30.535
- I don't know. I, I just
saw the tip of the fan.

23:44.424 --> 23:46.968
We should let them know, right?

23:47.052 --> 23:48.178
- Yeah.
- Nic!

23:49.846 --> 23:51.514
Nic, there's a shark!

23:59.356 --> 24:00.940
Nic, there's a shark!

24:02.567 --> 24:03.443
Come on! Nic!

24:06.571 --> 24:09.282
Look out! There's a shark!

24:09.366 --> 24:12.327
- Hi.

24:12.410 --> 24:13.620
Check this out.

24:13.703 --> 24:15.246
- There's a shark!

24:19.918 --> 24:22.587
Nic, come back! I
think I saw a shark!

24:22.671 --> 24:23.463
Come back!

25:02.711 --> 25:05.588
- I
can't see anything.

25:05.672 --> 25:07.257
- Okay.
- Stay calm.

25:08.466 --> 25:09.634
Don't splash.

25:38.538 --> 25:41.791
I didn't see anything.

25:59.601 --> 26:01.019
You saw a shark?

26:01.102 --> 26:02.103
- Annie did.

26:03.229 --> 26:04.022
- How big?

26:05.273 --> 26:07.984
- I don't know. I
just saw the tip.

26:08.068 --> 26:11.279
- It's probably a reefy.
There's lots of 'em around.

26:11.363 --> 26:12.864
- Yeah. They're mostly harmless.

26:14.282 --> 26:16.326
So many fish came through.

26:16.409 --> 26:18.620
- I know. Look what I scored.

26:18.703 --> 26:19.579
- Oh, wow.

26:22.999 --> 26:24.209
- It's almost lunch time.

26:24.292 --> 26:26.586
The sooner we get to the
island, sooner we eat.

26:27.754 --> 26:29.422
Nic, why don't
you and I go ahead

26:29.506 --> 26:30.924
and start cooking up this fish?

26:32.717 --> 26:34.844
- You sure you're okay?
- Yeah. I'm fine.

26:34.928 --> 26:37.013
I was just worried
about you guys.

26:37.097 --> 26:38.598
Go cook lunch. I'm starving.

26:39.432 --> 26:40.475
- Okay.

26:40.558 --> 26:41.976
- Okay?
- All right, let's go.

27:05.709 --> 27:06.751
Feeling better?

27:09.921 --> 27:11.214
- Yeah.

27:11.297 --> 27:12.090
- Nice.

27:18.430 --> 27:19.180
- You all good?

27:20.140 --> 27:21.433
- Yeah. I'm fine.

27:22.600 --> 27:23.560
- Is that the first
time you've met the man

27:23.643 --> 27:24.978
in the gray suit?

27:25.061 --> 27:26.771
- What?
- The man in the gray suit.

27:26.855 --> 27:28.857
That's what surfers call sharks.

27:28.940 --> 27:30.108
- Really?
- Yeah.

27:30.191 --> 27:31.693
I've seen a few.

27:31.776 --> 27:32.902
They're pretty timid usually.

27:32.986 --> 27:35.321
It's the big ones you
have to worry about.

28:49.896 --> 28:53.525
Lisa!

30:16.983 --> 30:18.026
Lisa.

30:20.236 --> 30:21.029
Lisa!

30:31.206 --> 30:32.582
Oh, Lisa!

30:36.086 --> 30:36.836
Lisa!

31:01.569 --> 31:03.029
- Annie!

31:20.046 --> 31:20.839
Annie!

31:42.193 --> 31:43.403
Oh my God!

32:07.135 --> 32:08.011
Annie!

33:05.735 --> 33:08.196
Shark!

33:10.490 --> 33:11.574
Shark! Shark!

33:17.288 --> 33:18.623
- Shit. What's going on?

33:18.707 --> 33:20.000
I'm going back.

33:22.085 --> 33:23.795
Come on. Let's go.

34:33.031 --> 34:33.822
- Lisa.

34:35.158 --> 34:36.993
Come on, swim to me.

34:42.248 --> 34:43.208
Lisa, come on.

34:45.543 --> 34:47.212
Lisa, focus on me. On me.

34:48.630 --> 34:49.630
Look at me.

34:51.675 --> 34:53.385
Come on, Lisa. Lisa!

34:54.594 --> 34:56.513
Swim to me. Swim to me.

34:59.766 --> 35:01.351
Keep coming, keep coming!

35:28.336 --> 35:30.213
Lisa, watch out!

35:32.590 --> 35:33.383
Lisa!

35:36.261 --> 35:37.303
Lisa!

35:40.473 --> 35:43.601
Oh, no.

35:46.396 --> 35:48.314
Where did you go?

35:48.398 --> 35:49.274
Lisa! Lisa!

36:02.829 --> 36:03.621
- Lisa!

36:05.123 --> 36:05.915
Lisa!

36:08.626 --> 36:09.419
Lisa!

36:10.754 --> 36:12.255
Lisa!

36:18.261 --> 36:19.054
Lisa!

36:45.705 --> 36:48.124
- Annie, we need
to flip the kayak.

36:48.208 --> 36:49.000
- Yeah.

36:50.168 --> 36:52.170
- Hey, you're gonna have
to get in the water.

36:56.257 --> 36:59.719
I'm gonna get in, we'll
turn it over, okay?

37:15.985 --> 37:19.322
Okay, okay.

37:20.365 --> 37:21.825
All right. Come on.

37:30.750 --> 37:31.543
Come on.

37:35.964 --> 37:37.382
Very good. Good.

37:42.554 --> 37:43.763
Get in. Quick.

37:52.689 --> 37:54.024
You okay? Okay.

38:22.844 --> 38:23.636
Hey.

38:26.890 --> 38:28.099
Hey, you okay?

38:30.352 --> 38:32.145
Honey, can you paddle?

38:34.064 --> 38:35.482
- Yeah.
- Yeah?

38:35.565 --> 38:36.983
Okay. Come on.

38:37.067 --> 38:39.069
- We have to get to the island.

38:39.152 --> 38:39.944
- That's where we're going.

38:40.028 --> 38:41.279
- No, I mean right now.

38:41.363 --> 38:43.531
