on that island.

38:48.370 --> 38:50.830
- Oh my God.

38:50.914 --> 38:52.248
Jodie! Jodie!

38:54.000 --> 38:55.502
There are kids in the water.

39:00.423 --> 39:01.800
- Oh my God. I'll go warn them.

39:01.883 --> 39:03.218
You stay with Annie.

39:07.806 --> 39:09.808
- Annie, can you paddle?

39:11.935 --> 39:13.269
- Yeah.

39:13.353 --> 39:15.563
- Okay, come on. Let's go.

39:17.148 --> 39:19.776
Yeah!

40:08.575 --> 40:10.285
Oh my God.

40:19.878 --> 40:22.839
Oh
my God. Oh my God.

40:22.922 --> 40:23.715
Oh my God.

40:29.387 --> 40:31.306
God.

40:31.389 --> 40:32.182
Oh my God.

40:55.580 --> 40:58.208
- Shark!

40:58.291 --> 40:59.000
Shark!

41:03.922 --> 41:05.340
Shark!

41:05.423 --> 41:06.966
See ya.

41:56.224 --> 41:57.475
- Shark! Shark!

41:58.393 --> 41:59.227
Mom, shark!

42:08.987 --> 42:10.071
Shark! Shark!

42:12.282 --> 42:13.575
- Shark! Shark!

42:14.534 --> 42:17.746
Shark, shark! Winston, hurry up!

42:19.330 --> 42:20.415
Faster! Faster!

42:20.498 --> 42:22.375
Winston! Come on, come!

42:39.934 --> 42:41.603
Stay there, Demi!

42:41.686 --> 42:43.396
Demi, don't move, don't move!

42:43.480 --> 42:44.856
Good girl!

43:47.085 --> 43:49.045
Oh my God.

43:56.261 --> 43:57.387
- Yeah. Good girl.

43:57.470 --> 43:58.722
Come on, come on, come on.

44:07.647 --> 44:09.858
Move, move faster, faster!

44:20.827 --> 44:22.203
Come on, here, gir

